<h3>Before you begin (prerequisites)</h3>
<div class="info-text">
</div>

<p>To create a new account, you will need the following:</p>
<ul>
  <li>An official contractor or government email preferred.</li>
  <li><span class="p1-required">* </span>Your onboarding supervisor present or readily available (to request access to necessary teams).</li>
  <li><span class="p1-required">* </span>If you need IL4+, you need Appgate installed on your computer.</li>
  <li><span class="p1-required">* </span>Your Common Access Card (CAC) connected to your device.</li>
  <li><span class="p1-required">* </span>If you don't have CAC yet, you need MFA app (Google Authenticator, Microsoft Authenticator)</li>
</ul>
<p class="description"><span class="p1-required">* </span>Only required if accessing other P1 solutions like ChatOps or PartyBus.</p>
<h3>Additional help</h3>
<p>If you experience any account issues, please contact the Platform One Help Desk by emailing <a href="mailto:${msg("helpEmail")}">${msg("helpEmail")}</a></p>
<p>If you do not know who your onboarding supervisor is for your team or need to add one, please contact the Party Bus Onboarding team by emailing <a href="mailto:aflcmc.hncx.p1-pbo@us.af.mil">aflcmc.hncx.p1-pbo@us.af.mil</a></p>
<p>You can also visit <a href="/auth/realms/${realm.name}/onboarding/faq" target="_blank">registration FAQ</a></p>
